{"tid":1698393,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周子瑜同老師超出師生關係","createTime":"2019-11-07T12:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T22:05:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b649e64dfd199c676e54f4e2c870dcc10bae4d44","tid":1698393,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3373/d3373759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3373%2Fd3373759.jpg&h=7dde9311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲嘻小瓜曾是子瑜的舞蹈老師。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／kuakua_0629、嘻小瓜提供）<br />\n<br />\n照片中，可以看到嘻小瓜彎下膝蓋，輕輕扶著扮成黑魔女的子瑜，「主人～～終於帶我出門囉～～～」，師徒間的互動相當逗趣。之所以現在才放合照，他解釋是因為想等剪好影片再一起和網友分享。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4492/d4492508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4492%2Fd4492508.jpg&h=fae652a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲嘻小瓜日前飛往南韓參加TWICE的4週年見面會。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／kuakua_0629）<br />\n<br />\n雖然每年只能見面一次，但絲毫不影響感情，嘻小瓜透露之前在後台見面的時間都很短暫，根本沒辦法好好和子瑜聊天，這次剛好有空檔一起吃飯分享近況，「聊天完發現我們都長大了，這種感覺真的很特別，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不再是老師與學生關係，更是貼近朋友間的相處</span></ins></strong>，真的很棒，7年還能保持關心跟聯絡真的很開心。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3679/d3679761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3679%2Fd3679761.jpg&h=64900d15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲嘻小瓜和子瑜無話不談。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／kuakua_0629）<br />\n<br />\n分享文讓不少粉絲看得很動容，相當羨慕嘻小瓜和子瑜私底下的真摯友誼，但也有部分網友故意酸他蹭熱度，對於無理批評，他不但沒有動怒，反而Tag對方帳號給予鼓勵，「下次你也可以去呀！」並附上一個比讚的符號，高EQ讓人很佩服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4492/d4492509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4492%2Fd4492509.jpg&h=364c5237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲嘻小瓜高EQ回應酸民。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／kuakua_0629）"},{"pid":"d3e76c498ca18d249fb7ffb7884623ff4a597c63","tid":1698393,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"95d17d618d93681968b0f2cd71ff85a426f69fe6","tid":1698393,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c83b59bd31dd699f1c3e5fe515e0f06ab125ce1","tid":1698393,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0279467a75d2c957214e37a9b250693f85d00440","tid":1698393,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"成個hiuyong咁撚樣 收皮啦好嗎"},{"pid":"d98bff183b5dbe6ed8cc3b55eeb4f0c12eea3604","tid":1698393,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"個鼻....."},{"pid":"4eb8e3f8b2d5067a1af94f8bf455d0b3b44719b8","tid":1698393,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"應該細個就咩過嚟...條友個樣貢變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901b0d696610a7e264e4ac76c637b4dc68e2b089","tid":1698393,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:44:32.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的仔"},{"pid":"74dc7bbb95c283e0079de13a5592e185bbcc3f22","tid":1698393,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c633a2fc96c0cbd99914b719371a71ce0b56b05","tid":1698393,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"樣衰到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c6be99ed2ed2a9c4c71f3d9aeedb0e425dd9c4","tid":1698393,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets